Title: Fix results in quicksearch if configured limit is reached
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1656680597
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.2.0b1

The quicksearch just returned a warning like "More than 80 results" if the
configured "Number of elements to show in Quicksearch" was reached.

This werk restores the behaviour from 1.6 versions. The configured number of
search results to show is now shown below this warning.

